An unforgettable journey at the International Makeup Carnival in Kolkata, where top cosmetics brands like Makeup Partner Forever 52 and Makeup Tools Partner London Prime India showcased their premium products. Thank you to Likka (Shale Ma’am) for her support. From professional-grade brushes to exclusive cosmetics, it was a paradise for makeup lovers! 💄✨
